{
  "stem": "10768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But still, one German train-- plane did, again-- just like when I ran in 1939-- again, they came very low and they started to shoot with, probably with a machine type of-- [SIGHS] we had to run off from the train.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lied down on the track.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And again, luckily nobody was killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went back on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it took awhile until we came to Kiwerce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Kiwerce was apparently-- we did not stay in the city Kiwerce, but we were told to locate in the woods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the trenches were made so that we could sleep-- it was made like a step, so we could put straw and maybe our knapsack under our head and cover ourselves with a coat.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were supposed to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At the hospital, I was assigned as a nurse to-- it was called the Sixth Hospital for Light Injuries.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were staying in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When the first rain came, the trenches were all filled up with water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was in spring 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was together there with Polish nurse, who was called Helinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And with Helinka, I became friendly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And usually either we slept near each other-- of course, we were sleeping, you know, as I told you, on the ground in the woods.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Helinka became sick of malaria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were others too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Somehow, with all the what I went through-- and then I went and I was working almost two months in that infectious disease hospital where a lot of nurses got-- became also sick, and died there from the-- I survived.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were in Kiwerce until the offensive started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't have too many patients there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
